<section class="page-hero">
  <div id="ambient-canvas" class="ambient-canvas"></div>
  <div class="container page-hero-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="legal-updated">Last updated: July 2026</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="legal-content">
  <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Contomatix ("we", "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use contomatix.com.</p>

  <h2>Information we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Contact form:</strong> when you submit our contact form, we collect your name, email address, and message so we can respond to your enquiry.</li>
    <li><strong>WhatsApp &amp; email:</strong> if you contact us directly, we receive the details you choose to share.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> like most websites, our hosting provider may log basic technical data (IP address, browser type, pages visited) for security and performance.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How we use your information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to your enquiries and provide our services.</li>
    <li>To prepare audits, proposals, and reports you request.</li>
    <li>To improve our website and services.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.</p>

  <h2>Data retention</h2>
  <p>We keep contact enquiries only as long as needed to handle your request or maintain our business relationship. You can ask us to delete your information at any time.</p>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>Our site loads fonts from Google Fonts and the Three.js library from a CDN. These providers may receive standard technical data (such as your IP address) when the resources load. Our contact form is delivered by email over an encrypted connection.</p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of the personal information we hold about you by emailing us.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:<%= site.contactEmail %>" style="color: var(--accent-teal-dim); font-weight: 600;"><%= site.contactEmail %></a> or reach us via the <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--accent-teal-dim); font-weight: 600;">contact page</a>.</p>
</div>
